{"content": "<p>Hugo Faz is a leading light for artists in emerging economies where exchange rates are the start of many significant hurdles in accessing the artist opportunity of NFTs. NU NFT is the incubator where you'll find art from a range of artists including <a href=\"https://foundation.app/@NU_NFT/~/103656\">Rony Hernandes</a>, <a href=\"https://foundation.app/@NU_NFT/~/93303\">Luiz Leles</a> and <a href=\"https://foundation.app/@jhen_scalco\">Jhen Scalco</a> thanks to <a href=\"https://foundation.app/@hugofaz\">Hugo Faz</a>. </p><blockquote class=\"kg-blockquote-alt\">\"The NFT art space is currently missing the best artists due to global asymmetries. NU NFT is an initiative — soon to become a full-fledged DAO.\" says Hugo.</blockquote><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-wide kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2021/12/Screen-Shot-2021-12-17-at-2.31.46-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1030\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2021/12/Screen-Shot-2021-12-17-at-2.31.46-PM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2021/12/Screen-Shot-2021-12-17-at-2.31.46-PM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2021/12/Screen-Shot-2021-12-17-at-2.31.46-PM.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2021/12/Screen-Shot-2021-12-17-at-2.31.46-PM.png 2342w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 1200px\"><figcaption>Artists in the NU NFT collective&nbsp;</figcaption></figure><p>Hugo is building a pipeline between art collectors and talent historically cut off from anything beyond their local gallery. Artists selected for the roster are almost exclusively women, bipoc and LGBTQ+ artists. Where English is a second language, Hugo lends a hand. Where gas fees for listing and selling are prohibitive, <a href=\"https://foundation.app/@nu_nft\">@nu_nft</a> foots the bill. If there was an individual that personifies the WAGMI spirit, it's Hugo Faz. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2021/12/nft.jpg-51.webp\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2021/12/nft.jpg-51.webp 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2021/12/nft.jpg-51.webp 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2021/12/nft.jpg-51.webp 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w2400/2021/12/nft.jpg-51.webp 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://foundation.app/@hugofaz/100nudeshoots/1\">Rebirth, with Rony Hernandes</a> by Hugo Faz on Foundation marketplace</figcaption></figure><p>Rebirth is the first in a series of <a href=\"https://foundation.app/collection/100nudeshoots\">100 Nude Shoots of Hugo</a> (photograph shot by Rony Hernandes) that will evolve through the newly released Foundation collection capability. Hugo has plenty to shortlist from 2020, where he created one nude self portrait every day of the year!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Gm<br /><br />This is me quite a few years younger, in a collaborative photoshoot with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/RonyHernandes?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@RonyHernandes</a>. We made this at the gm of both our artistic self-discovery journeys.<br /><br />2021 was a whole new beginning, so I chose this as genesis for 100 Nude Shoots as NFTs. +<a href=\"https://t.co/GHX9FdskL3\">https://t.co/GHX9FdskL3</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/21CGZnXGNh\">pic.twitter.com/21CGZnXGNh</a></p>&mdash; HugoFaz.eth - NU NFT (@HugoFaz) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/HugoFaz/status/1470784212974419981?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">December 14, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p>What is Hugo's posture when it comes to art? Look no further than his artist statement:</p><blockquote>\"Cutting-edge performance art permeates Hugo's 10 year body of work in photography and filmmaking, whether portraying the Brazilian queer art scene and its personalities, making censorship-defying artistic statements or via the creation of expanded-body personas, through which the artist immerses himself in themes of body, identity, human and human-machine relationship, bio/necropolitics and crypto.\"</blockquote><p>Censorship defying statements is what the blockchain was born for and why artwork like <a href=\"https://foundation.app/@NU_NFT/~/89115\">Brazilla</a> is made possible. Brazil's president Bolsanaro's response, or lack thereof and the resulting 700,000 deaths is minted as a reminder of how voices can sway how we perceive the world around us. </p><blockquote class=\"kg-blockquote-alt\">\"We believe freedom will only be possible when the margins engulf the center.\" says Hugo. </blockquote><p>'<a href=\"https://foundation.app/@NU_NFT/~/92582\">A gm hopeful</a>' was the first time MintFace discovered Hugo's creativity in curating the <a href=\"https://oncyber.io/6529gm\">6529 gm Gallery</a>. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-wide kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2021/12/Screen-Shot-2021-12-17-at-2.49.10-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"999\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2021/12/Screen-Shot-2021-12-17-at-2.49.10-PM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2021/12/Screen-Shot-2021-12-17-at-2.49.10-PM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2021/12/Screen-Shot-2021-12-17-at-2.49.10-PM.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w2400/2021/12/Screen-Shot-2021-12-17-at-2.49.10-PM.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 1200px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://foundation.app/@NU_NFT/~/92582\">a gm hopeful by Hugo Faz</a> on Foundation marketplace</figcaption></figure><p>Each artwork made possible by NU NFT writes the royalty split directly into the contract. When photographer and Brazilian artist Jhen Scalco sells <a href=\"https://foundation.app/@NU_NFT/~/110717\">Shadow Dress</a>, 50% of earnings go directly in to her wallet. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2021/12/Screen-Shot-2021-12-17-at-2.30.10-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1016\" height=\"1122\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2021/12/Screen-Shot-2021-12-17-at-2.30.10-PM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2021/12/Screen-Shot-2021-12-17-at-2.30.10-PM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2021/12/Screen-Shot-2021-12-17-at-2.30.10-PM.png 1016w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>These eth funds are crucial for artists to mint and list their next work. The remaining 50% goes back into the <a href=\"https://foundation.app/@NU_NFT\">@nu_NFT</a> fund to assist artists mint their genesis. Here's the list of artists to follow on Foundation so far:</p><p><a href=\"https://foundation.app/@stevenb\">3stelAd4n</a> is the cryptoartist persona for Hugo Faz and Steven B, a queer performance and visual artist duo from Brazil delving in themes of body, identity, bio and necropolitics.</p><p><a href=\"https://foundation.app/@jhen_scalco\">Jhen Scalco</a> - her work is charged with symbology and affective meaning, drawing a high dose of intimacy over a fine line between fiction and reality.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"pt\" dir=\"ltr\">Uma pequena série de imagens pra mostrar um pouco das minhas artes (tem quem ache coisa de doido, e é). Este autorretrato sou eu todinha. <a href=\"https://t.co/XboeHRAc8i\">pic.twitter.com/XboeHRAc8i</a></p>&mdash; Jhen Scalco (@jhen_scalco) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jhen_scalco/status/1462474276301426690?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November\n 21, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p><a href=\"https://foundation.app/@LuizLeles\">Luiz Leles</a> - Fine Art Photographer. Creator. Writer.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">WOW!!! <a href=\"https://twitter.com/PlayboyNFTS?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@PlayboyNFTS</a> just bid on WAGMI, our genesis piece in collab with Luiz Leles! Auction is live!<br /><br />NU NFT proceeds are totally reapplied to curate/incubate/mint/launch many more peripheric Brazilian artists to NFTs to finally get recognition. BID ON!!<a href=\"https://t.co/ZEesy6ak6u\">https://t.co/ZEesy6ak6u</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/Rjp858MPuA\">pic.twitter.com/Rjp858MPuA</a></p>&mdash; HugoFaz.eth - NU NFT (@HugoFaz) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/HugoFaz/status/1454140669925199883?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 29, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p> <a href=\"https://foundation.app/@ronyhernandes\">Rony Hernandes</a> - Artista. A promising 24 year-old award winning creative photographer.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">good morning <a href=\"https://t.co/WKIhl0PUeB\">pic.twitter.com/WKIhl0PUeB</a></p>&mdash; Rony, Júnior ou Hernandes (@RonyHernandes) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/RonyHernandes/status/1469679868065595402?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">December 11, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p><a href=\"https://foundation.app/@nu_nft\">Hugo Faz</a> - Photographer, Performance Artist, Collector.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"und\" dir=\"ltr\">gm <a href=\"https://t.co/JJdBRJ0P3I\">pic.twitter.com/JJdBRJ0P3I</a></p>&mdash; HugoFaz.eth - NU NFT (@HugoFaz) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/HugoFaz/status/1471086559436943365?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">December 15, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">There’s one more thing: I’ll be experimenting with different original collaborative token mint dynamics in the 100NUDES collection in a way that my collectors will be co-creating the project’s narrative with me. + <a href=\"https://t.co/KDTvMx0L7G\">pic.twitter.com/KDTvMx0L7G</a></p>&mdash; HugoFaz.eth - NU NFT (@HugoFaz) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/HugoFaz/status/1470784252686082054?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">December 14, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p></p><hr /><p>Receive new artist features by email.</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-left\"><a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/#/portal/signup\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Subscribe to MintFace</a></div><div class=\"kg-card kg-callout-card kg-callout-card-pink\"><div class=\"kg-callout-emoji\">💡</div><div class=\"kg-callout-text\"><strong>Artists. Join the next <a href=\"https://maven.com/mintface/nft-digital-artist-economy\">Digital Artist Economy Accelerator</a> </strong>and launch your NFT collection with confidence on your own smart contract.</div></div><div class=\"kg-card kg-callout-card kg-callout-card-purple\"><div class=\"kg-callout-emoji\">💡</div><div class=\"kg-callout-text\"><strong>Collectors. </strong><a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/#/portal/signup\">Subscribe to MintFace Premium</a> for $USD9 per month. MintFace surfaces great artists and artworks so you don't have to.</div></div>"}